---
import '../styles/global.css';
import Downloader from '../components/react/downloads/Downloader.tsx';
---

<html class="dark" lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
    <title>Spotiyei - Descarga tu música</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Spline+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 antialiased font-display">
    <div class="relative flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col overflow-x-hidden">
        <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-primary/10 bg-background-light/80 dark:bg-background-dark/80 backdrop-blur-md px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40 py-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-primary">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl font-bold">album</span>
                    <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Spotiyei</h2>
                </div>
                </div>
        </header>

        <main class="flex-1">
            <section class="relative px-6 py-20 md:py-32 hero-gradient overflow-hidden">
                <div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto text-center flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
      
                    <h1 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight max-w-4xl">
                        Descarga tu mundo en <span class="text-primary">Spotify</span>.
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl font-normal max-w-2xl">
                        Convierte tus playlists, álbumes y canciones favoritas a MP3 de alta calidad al instante. Sin instalaciones.
                    </p>

                    <Downloader client:load />

                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 translate-x-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
            </section>

            <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-background-dark/50">
                <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-center mb-16">
                        <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">Lleva tu música a cualquier parte</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg">Tres sencillos pasos para disfrutar de tu biblioteca sin conexión.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                        <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/10 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all duration-300">
                            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">content_paste</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">1. Pega el enlace</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                                Ve a Spotify, copia el enlace de cualquier canción o playlist y pégalo en nuestro buscador.
                            </p>
                            <span class="absolute top-4 right-8 text-6xl font-black text-primary/5 select-none">01</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/10 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all duration-300">
                            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">tune</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">2. Procesamiento</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                                Nuestro servidor busca automáticamente la mejor calidad de audio disponible y la convierte a MP3.
                            </p>
                            <span class="absolute top-4 right-8 text-6xl font-black text-primary/5 select-none">02</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/10 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all duration-300">
                            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">download_done</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">3. Descarga</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                                Recibirás un archivo listo para reproducir en tu reproductor de música favorito.
                            </p>
                            <span class="absolute top-4 right-8 text-6xl font-black text-primary/5 select-none">03</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-background-dark px-6 py-12 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-primary/5">
            <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-6">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-primary">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl font-bold">school</span>
                    <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Proyecto Educativo</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm max-w-md leading-relaxed">
                    Aplicación construida con fines didácticos. Demostración práctica de APIs, Web Scraping, React y Python.
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-600 text-xs mt-4">
                    © 2026 Spotiyei. Sin afiliación con Spotify AB. Uso estrictamente educativo.
                </p>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>